data.description: Your not going to want to miss this one!!  Turnkey and investor ready with newer furniture and appliances included! Located in the highly sought after community of Southern Dunes Golf and Country Club. Homes here do not last long! This spectacular pool home has it all and the owner's have made this home shine! From its relaxing heated swimming pool laid with elegant blue glass tiles, to it's absolutely stunning interior with porcelain tile and textured ceilings the owner has absolutely adored this home and has customized it to a new level of beauty and it shows! Upstairs this beautiful home boasts 2 large guest bedrooms and an extra large master-suite with it's own private garden tub. Downstairs there's a 4th room that would make the perfect office or 4th bedroom. Come live the dream and enjoy some of Florida's perfect year-round weather or make this one the perfect vacation home and high-end rental property. Short term bookings allowed! Southern Dunes Golf & Country Club encompasses one the most stunning and pristine 18 hole golf courses in all of Florida. Don't miss your opportunity come see this one before it's gone! Schedule your showing today!!
